Glest source code is GPL (see file COPYING for license). For the data you can do whatever you want with it as long as you give the creator credit; This will work fine with nearly every open source license GPL/BSD/CreativeCommon. Only Public Domain will not work, as it has not credits.

Glest is copyright of the Glest Team ( http://glest.org/en/credits.php ). Glest Advanced Engine (GAE) is forked from Glest 3.1.2.

